ke their debut on stage, symbolizing a fusion of fashion and music at its finest.<br><br>In addition, Jaspal will release a limited-edition merchandise collection, available only at the concert. Featuring designs inspired by the spirit of the band and the legacy of their music, this exclusive line is made for fans and fashion collectors alike — a tribute to a night that promises to be truly unforgettable.<br><br>Join us as we celebrate the comeback of Groove Riders, where music and style unite in a once-in-a-lifetime experience — powered by Jaspal.</span></p></div></section><section data-section-id="pf-49d5" data-pf-type="FlexSection" class="sc-hceuva jkduKR pf-15_"><div class="sc-jeyqhx gyoqcw pf-flex-section"><img alt="Jaspal_x_SS25_GR_Page_Cover.jpg__PID:3a55467b-214d-43d7-99ce-0af5116d60f4" src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0753/8576/6127/files/Jaspal_x_SS25_GR_Page_Cover.jpg?v=1753846761&width=2048" srcSet="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0753/8576/6127/files/Jaspal_x_SS25_GR_Page_Cover.jpg?v=1753846761&width=375 375w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0753/8576/6127/files/Jaspal_x_SS25_GR_Page_Cover.jpg?v=1753846761&width=550 550w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0753/8576/6127/files/Jaspal_x_SS25_GR_Page_Cover.jpg?v=1753846761&width=768 768w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0753/8576/6127/files/Jaspal_x_SS25_GR_Page_Cover.jpg?v=1753846761&width=1024 1024w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0753/8576/6127/files/Jaspal_x_SS25_GR_Page_Cover.jpg?v=1753846761&width=1280 1280w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0753/8576/6127/files/Jaspal_x_SS25_GR_Page_Cover.jpg?v=1753846761&width=1440 1440w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0753/8576/6127/files/Jaspal_x_SS25_GR_Page_Cover.jpg?v=1753846761&width=1680 1680w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0753/8576/6127/files/Jaspal_x_SS25_GR_Page_Cover.jpg?v=1753846761&width=1800 1800w,https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0753/8576/6127/files/Jaspal_x_SS25_GR_Page_Cover.jpg?v=1753846761&width=1920 1920w,https://cdn.shopify.co